# Momo AI Deep Dive

## About
The "Momo AI Deep Dive" is a monthly workshop series in Salzburg, Austria, focused on Advanced AI Skills, Coding, and Automation. It is hosted by Momo Feichtinger (Strategenwerk).

## Core Topics
- **AI Coding**: Moving from using tools to building software.
- **Automation**: Automating workflows with AI.
- **RAG & Vector DBs**: Building custom knowledge bases.
- **Agentic AI**: Creating autonomous agents.
